reviewText: I got just what I expected, a quality product. Oliver North loves America and has obvious love and respect for the military

My husband is an Army Special Forces soldier in 5th special forces group and is very proud to be a part of something so important to the world. This documentary gave an eye opening, inside look of what US Army Special Forces is all about. It shines a very positive light on the hard work these men perform every day in multiple countries around the world. They are TRUELY heroes and Oliver North did a wonderful job of showcasing their talents.
